      • getLocalVariables

        public LocalVariable[] getLocalVariables()
        Returns an array containing all local variables. Each local variable is contained at the position of it's index. If no debug information is available for some variables, then the array contains holes. Be aware of that! And please don't modify the array. I don't want to wrap it in an UnmodifiableList containing an ArrayList (from Arrays.asList()). For performance reasons I just return the bare array.
        Returns:
        an unmodifiable list of all local variables
